  "title": "Lios Hobbit Hill Village",
  "description": "Adds cozy, hidden hill villages with grassy rooftops and expansive underground homes",
  "body": "<p><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/JFF7vxPq/Lios-Outlandish-Village-1.png\" alt=\"Lios-Outlandish-Village-1\" border=\"0\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Discover a charming hobbit-inspired village nestled inside a lush hill, filled with cozy homes and lively villagers. Explore the beautifully lit cavern interiors, relax by the pond up top, and keep an eye out for a secret button&mdash;find it to unlock a treasure vault these villagers have hidden away!</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/Gf1cvJrc/hobbit-hill-village1.png\" alt=\"hobbit-hill-village1\" border=\"0\">\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/hF2zfm5S/hobbit-hill-village2.png\" alt=\"hobbit-hill-village2\" border=\"0\">\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/JwN8ntsg/hobbit-hill-village3.png\" alt=\"hobbit-hill-village3\" border=\"0\">\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/cX8w2qp6/hobbit-hill-village4.png\" alt=\"hobbit-hill-village4\" border=\"0\">\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/6c5wbRss/hobbit-hill-village5.png\" alt=\"hobbit-hill-village5\" border=\"0\">\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/LDk5N4F0/hobbit-hill-village6.png\" alt=\"hobbit-hill-village6\" border=\"0\">\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/zWJBBNpj/hobbit-hill-village7.png\" alt=\"hobbit-hill-village7\" border=\"0\">\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/8n706pcv/hobbit-hill-village8.png\" alt=\"hobbit-hill-village8\" border=\"0\">\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/3554tgPC/hobbit-hill-village9.png\" alt=\"hobbit-hill-village9\" border=\"0\">\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://i.ibb.co/vC3r8VSc/compatibility.png\" alt=\"compatibility\" width=\"449\" height=\"41\" border=\"0\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>These do not overhaul existing vanilla villages, making them compatible with any other village overhaul mod such as <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/lios-overhauled-villages\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Lio's Overhauled Villages</a>! Part of a new series, Lio's Outlandish Villages aims to bring uniquely styles townes and adventurous builds to explore!</em></p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://i.ibb.co/m5LGyB8T/morefromthisseries.png\" alt=\"morefromthisseries\" width=\"586\" height=\"36\" border=\"0\"></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/spiral-tower-villages\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"> <img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://i.ibb.co/qLJcs1SQ/spiral-towers.png\" alt=\"spiral-towers\" width=\"376\" height=\"62\" border=\"0\"> </a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div style=\"max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 14px 16px; border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.12); border-radius: 12px; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.03);\">\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/lioloader\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px; text-decoration: none;\">\n    <img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/wrK85wgc/logo.png\" alt=\"LioLoader\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" style=\"display:block; border-radius: 12px;\">\n    <div style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.35;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; color: inherit;\">Need datapack-based configuration?</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 14px; color: inherit; opacity: 0.9;\">\n        Check out <strong>LioLoader</strong> for global datapack / resource pack loading. Available for <strong>NeoForge</strong> and <strong>Fabric</strong> on <strong>Minecraft 1.21.x</strong>.\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 13px; color: inherit; opacity: 0.85; margin-top: 4px;\">Open LioLoader on Modrinth →</div>\n    </div>\n  </a>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://i.ibb.co/fV6VtS4Q/youtube-reviews.png\" alt=\"youtube-reviews\" width=\"605\" height=\"44\"></p>\n<details>\n<summary>Spoiler</summary>\n<p>-Reviewed At 11:59-<br><iframe title=\"TOP 15 NEW Minecraft Mods Of The Month! (1.21.8 to 1.20.1) | July\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/rM1fSI28POk?start=719\" width=\"854\" height=\"480\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n</details>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2><a href=\"https://discord.com/invite/pGkUmgGcsY\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://i.ibb.co/qDNhg49/636e0a6a49cf127bf92de1e2-icon-clyde-blurple-RGB.png\" width=\"128\" height=\"97\"></a></h2>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://i.ibb.co/hJvQHRN5/usageinmodpacks.png\" alt=\"usageinmodpacks\" width=\"573\" height=\"39\" border=\"0\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Feel free to include the <strong>Hobbit Hill Village</strong> in any Minecraft modpack of your choice. We encourage you to build unique and engaging adventures by incorporating these structures into your customized packs. No need to request permission&mdash;just explore and enjoy the villages however you like!</p>",
